DietPi - dietpi.com


Steps to install the DietPi image for the Raspberry Pi:

  1. Download the image from dietpi.com
     initial username: root
     initial password: dietpi

  2. Using Etcher (https://etcher.io/), write to the SD card
  
  3. Plug the micro SD card into the Raspberry Pi. Turn on the Raspberry Pi
  
  4. Obtain the device's public IP address through the router for SSH (Secure Socket Shell)
     *Ensure port forwarding is turned on through the router
     
  5. Using Terminal:
     'SSH root@IP ADDRESS'
     
